{"sections":[],"metadata":{"title":"requestProgress","roleHeading":"Instance Method","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack(im)requestProgress","symbolKind":"method"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"requestProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state and progress of an inactive or completed pack are computed lazily. If"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"you need the state or progress of a pack whose "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" property is currently"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set to "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"},{"type":"text","text":", observe KVO change notifications on this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" key path, then call this method. Alternatively, you can add an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"observer for "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification"},{"type":"text","text":" about this pack that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"come from the default notification center."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePack","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackState/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"It is unknown whether the pack is inactive, active, or complete."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate\/mlnofflinepackstateunknown","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Posted by the shared "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" object when an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object’s progress changes. The progress may change due to a resource being"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"downloaded or because the pack discovers during the download that more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"resources are required for offline viewing. This notification is posted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whenever any field in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" property changes."}],"title":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackprogresschangednotification","kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack/requestProgress":{"title":"requestProgress","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"requestProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Request an asynchronous update to the pack’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"state"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"progress"},{"type":"text","text":" properties."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack\/requestprogress"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"title":"MapLibre"}}}